@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #79224 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
Seems like P-low. You can repro on stable, but it requires nightly features.
I agree with a P-low, I see the discussion on the min_specialization is still in flux (currently debating American or British spelling :laughing: )
I will tentatively assign a P-low but open to a re-evaluation
